item.description: A Game Studio where we train enthusiastic students to develop mobile games and help them launch their games in app stores. We are a team of young and motivated people based around the city of Pokhara. Together with our expertise in several domains of software design, development and marketing, we are headed for a common goal of touching as many life as possible through our products. Thank you!
